    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This car is an absolute dream! I\u2019ve babied it since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, and it still has that fresh new-car smell inside. It drives so smoothly, you\u2019ll honestly forget it\u2019s even had a previous owner. I'm so excited for someone to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. You've really gotta see this one in person to believe how gorgeous it is!",
